Tingnan mo, guro.

747
00:55:16.522 --> 00:55:19.061
Manatiling malapit kay Professor Song.

748
00:55:19.061 --> 00:55:20.247
Hindi mo alam.

749
00:55:20.247 --> 00:55:22.282
Halika, ako?

750
00:55:23.361 --> 00:55:25.941
Ngayong tapos ka na, kumain na tayo.

751
00:55:25.941 --> 00:55:29.490
Sorry, may klase ako.
kaya kailangan kong pumunta sa Ansan.

752
00:55:29.490 --> 00:55:31.591
Sige.

