Hindi, hindi ko nakalimutan.

768
00:56:45.899 --> 00:56:47.234
- Umalis ka.
- Magandang araw.

769
00:56:47.234 --> 00:56:49.069
paalam na.

770
00:56:49.907 --> 00:56:51.905
<i>Sa tingin ko mahuhuli ako.</i>

771
00:56:51.905 --> 00:56:53.407
<i>Maraming traffic.</i>

772
00:56:53.407 --> 00:56:55.512
At ang mga bulaklak? Nakuha mo ba sila?

773
