774
00:56:57.206 --> 00:56:58.901
<i>Matagal akong makakahanap ng florist.</i>

775
00:56:58.901 --> 00:57:00.184
ayos lang.

776
00:57:00.184 --> 00:57:02.716
Bibilhin ko sila, dumating ka sa lalong madaling panahon.

777
00:57:02.716 --> 00:57:03.986
Mag-ingat sa pagmamaneho,

778
00:57:03.986 --> 00:57:06.019
